ines. Our ETOpen Ruleset is available for download any time.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-07-19T14:48:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sbilly/awesome-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Network</h2><h3>Security Information &#x26; Event Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.prelude-siem.org/\">Prelude</a> - Prelude is a Universal \"Security Information &#x26; Event Management\" (SIEM) system. Prelude collects, normalizes, sorts, aggregates, correlates and reports all security-related events independently of the product brand or license giving rise to such events; Prelude is \"agentless\".</li>","updatedAt":"2017-07-19T14:43:23.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sbilly/awesome-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Big Data</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/apache/incubator-metron\">Apache Metron (incubating)</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/apache/incubator-metron\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">825</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":825,\"repo\":\"apache/incubator-metron\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Metron integrates a variety of open source big data technologies in order to offer a centralized tool for security monitoring and analysis.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-07-19T14:35:46.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sbilly/awesome-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Big Data</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/apache/incubator-spot\">Apache Spot (incubating)</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/apache/incubator-spo